           queue(mtTPL)                             *** Queue
           rapi                                     *** REST API
           worker(mtTPL)                            *** Worker 0
           worker(mtTPL)                            *** Worker 1
           log(mtJL)                                *** Log
           clock(0, random(counter) rem max, max)   *** Clock
           .
endm

